"" markdown設定
augroup AuAddMdSpace
  autocmd!
  autocmd BufWrite *.md call g:add_md_space()
augroup END

"" ruby設定
" Buffer保存後にvim-ruby経由のmakeを走らせ,再描画
augroup AuRbSyntaxCheck
  autocmd!
  autocmd BufWritePost *.rb silent make -c % | redraw!
augroup END

"" quickfix設定
" makeしたらquickfixリストを表示:
augroup AuQuickFixOpen
  autocmd!
  autocmd QuickfixCmdPost make cw
augroup END
